values: 跳跃；跳过；略过；忽略；跳绳；轻快地蹦跳；蹦蹦跳跳地走；快速转移；悄悄溜走；不参加；缺席；逃避；不做（应做的事等）；打水漂；（在水面上）掠过；（心脏）漏跳
跳跃；蹦跳；跳过；废料桶；倾倒箱

word_mean_info__list.difference: 指两脚交替轻地跳或跨的动作。
指单脚短跳或双足猛力的动作。也指小鸟、青蛙等的跳。
更强调有力和弹跳的运动。
多指向前向上或向下跳跃、奔跳。
常可与jump换用，但侧重身体猛力向上升起并朝前急冲的动作，有时含突然的意味。
是普通用词，指用双脚向上跳，向下跳，或在同一平面上跳到有一定距离的某一点上，或跳过。

word_group.brief_definition: (粗暴地表示不想谈论或重复说)别提这事儿, 不说这个了

bilingual.source: Don't skip the instructions; they are important.
bilingual.target: 不要跳过说明；它们很重要。

bilingual.source: She decided to skip the meeting and work from home.
bilingual.target: 她决定跳过会议，在家工作。

bilingual.source: I always skip breakfast because I'm in a hurry.
bilingual.target: 我总是跳过早餐，因为我很赶时间。

bilingual.source: You can skip the nonessential parts of the meeting.
bilingual.target: 你可以跳过会议中非必要的部分。

bilingual.source: The survey includes facultative questions that you can skip.
bilingual.target: 调查包括一些可选择的问题，你可以跳过。

bilingual.source: She was tempted to skip her workout and watch TV instead.
bilingual.target: 她被诱惑跳过锻炼而去看电视。

list.abstract: Skip（[skɪp]），英语单词。作动词为轻快地蹦跳；错过。作名词为蹦跳；跳跃。短语搭配有skip rope（跳绳）。例句为“She began to skip down the path.（她开始沿着小路蹦跳。）” Skip的及物动词近义词有dance；不及物动词近义词有clear；名词近义词有spring。

yingyinNormal.en: What isn't? Always saying "No" to things and then eventually coming around. Why can't we just skip to the good part?
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么特质？就总是先拒绝一切，虽然最终总会想通。我们为什么不能跳过不讨喜的部分呢？

yingyinNormal.en: We'll skip the details and assume you had a long, fulfilling life so we can get to what is really important -- how you die.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们把细节跳过，假设你拥有长久而幸福的一生然后再来看看最关键的部分——你怎么死的。

yingyinNormal.en: You can skip whatever formal hooey it takes to join 'cause we're gonna run this club. This is known as the Smackle theory of inevitability.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们可以直接跳过那些加入社团的繁文缛节，因为我们会成为社团的领导者，这就是所谓的史麦科必然性理论。

yingyinNormal.en: Beverly, you know I hold you in high esteem. Can we skip the part where you pretend not to know the answer, and get to the part where you tell me the answer?
yingyinNormal.zh: 贝弗利，你知道我十分敬重你。我们可以跳过你假装不知道答案的戏码，直接进入你告诉我答案的环节吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Proceed. Good afternoon. Skip to the end.
yingyinNormal.zh: 继续吧。下午好。跳到重点。

yingyinNormal.en: Just going to skip over that insult. What insult? Yeah! That's why I'm going to skip over it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这句侮辱我就当没听到吧。什么侮辱？没错，所以我才要假装没听到。

yingyinNormal.en: I like sand. I like sea. I like Suzy to skip with me. I like ping. I like pang. I like Zoe to skip along.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我喜欢大地，我喜欢海洋，我喜欢苏西和我一起跳。我喜欢乒。我喜欢乓。我喜欢佐伊和我一起跳。

yingyinNormal.en: Actually, we're going to have to skip the dance class today.
yingyinNormal.zh: 事实上 今天我们不会去上舞蹈课

yingyinNormal.en: So, you agree with my friends that I should skip the premiere?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以你也同意他们的话，我不应该去看首映吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, you look tired, Daddy Pig. Oh, I'm fine. I could skip to a hundred.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，你看上去很累了，猪爸爸。噢，我没事的，我可以跳一百个的。

yingyinNormal.en: It is play time. Rebecca Rabbit, Zoe Zebra, Suzy sheep and Peppa all like to skip.
yingyinNormal.zh: 游戏时间到了。小兔瑞贝卡，斑马佐伊，小样苏西还有佩奇都喜欢跳绳。

yingyinNormal.en: Mom, we could've skipped all this. We still could skip it if you'll just give me the photos.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈，我们可以省去这些，只要你把那些照片给我，我们可以省去这些事。

yingyinNormal.en: I had more prepared, but I'm just gonna skip to the rings and vows, since I've been answering your questions for 45 minutes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我本来准备了更多证婚词，但我决定直接跳到交换戒指与婚誓部分，因为我在这里回答了45分钟你们的问题。

yingyinNormal.en: I know. Let's see who can skip the most without stopping. I'll count. One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道了。我们来比一下看谁能跳绳跳得更多。我来数数。一，二，三，四，五，六，七，八，九，十。

yingyinNormal.en: I can't go to bed yet. I haven't got a talent to show tomorrow. But you have lots of talents, Peppa. Yes, I can skip. I can sing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我现在还不可以睡觉，我还没有想好明天要表演什么才艺。但是你有很多才艺可以表演啊，佩奇。我可以跳绳。我还可以唱歌。

yingyinNormal.en: I was going to skip, or sing, or dance! But they have all been done. A talent can be anything, Peppa. But not watching television.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我本来打算跳绳，唱歌，或者跳舞。但是大家都表演过了。佩奇，才艺可以是任何事。但是看电视可不算是一个才艺哦。

yingyinNormal.en: Actually, we can't skip the dance class today. We have a big recital coming up. We're doing an excerpt from Swan Lake. Yeah, Swan Lake!
yingyinNormal.zh: 事实上 我们今天必须去上舞蹈课，我们马上就要有个盛大的公演了，我们在排练《天鹅湖》的片段 。没错 《天鹅湖》

yingyinNormal.en: Leonard, I'm no expert here, but I believe in the context of a luncheon invitation, you might want to skip the reference to bowel movements.
yingyinNormal.zh: 莱纳德，这方面我不在行，不过我相信如果是邀请别人吃午餐，你最好不要说些肠运动的事。

yingyinNormal.en: The movie starts in 17 minutes, which means we'll need to make all the lights on Colorado Boulevard, plus skip the concession stand, and preshow urination.
yingyinNormal.zh: 电影17分钟后开始，也就是说我们得赶上科罗拉多大道的全部绿灯，而且不能去买东西吃了，开场前也不能去尿尿了。

yingyinNormal.en: Fine. That sounds great. All right. Okay, fine. No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no! I know I seem like the last person to say this, but we can't just skip Thanksgiving!
yingyinNormal.zh: 好啊，是个好主意。好吧，行。不，不，不要，我知道我一般不会说这种话的，但我们不能直接略过感恩节啊。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: to leave out something that would normally be the next thing that you would do, read, etc.

examination_example.sentence: Students can easily <highlight>skip</highlight> half their homework and see very little difference on their report cards.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 学生能轻易跳过一半的家庭作业，而这在成绩报告单上几乎看不出任何区别。

sense_info_list.en: to move forwards lightly and quickly making a little jump with each step

examination_example.sentence: Losing a job is hurting: you don't <highlight>skip</highlight> down to the jobcentre with a song in your heart.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 失业是痛苦的：你不可能在心头哼着歌，跳着去就业中心。

sense_info_list.en: to not do something that you usually do or should do
to move from one place to another or from one subject to another very quickly

word_usage.usage:
skip和jump都可以表示“跳”，区别在于：
jump是一种不带有感情色彩的动作，如跳远就要用jump。
skip更多带着一种快乐轻松的情绪，是指人或者动物“轻盈，轻快，迅速地蹦”。
skip还有“跳过，省略，遗漏”等拓展含义，如skip over/through译为“划过，省略”

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: bound off one point after another intentionally

examination_example.sentence: More of them will <highlight>skip</highlight> those calculations altogether and just power through the holidays into 2017.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们中的更多人将完全跳过这些计算，只在假期中工作到2017年。

examination_example.sentence: Their risky behaviors—drinking too much alcohol, using illegal drugs, smoking cigarettes and <highlight>skipping</highlight> school—can alert parents and teachers that serious problems are brewing.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们的危险行为——酗酒、使用非法药物、吸烟和逃学——可以提醒家长和老师，严重的问题正在酝酿之中。

examination_example.sentence: The population of digital video recorders has caused advertisers to worry that their commercials will be <highlight>skipped</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 数码录像机的数量之多，让广告客户担心他们的广告会被跳过。

sense_info_list.en: move along lightly, stepping from one foot to the other with a hop or bounce

direction_info.description:

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: fail to attend or deal with as appropriate
bound off one point after another intentionally

examination_example.sentence: Many of us grow up believing that <highlight>skipping</highlight> breakfast is a serious mistake, even if only two thirds of adults in the UK eat breakfast regularly, according to the British Dietetic Association, and around three-quarters of Americans.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 即使我们很多人从小就认为，不吃早餐是一个严重的错误，但是根据英国饮食协会的统计，英国只有三分之二的成年人经常吃早餐，美国人约有四分之三。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Skipping</highlight> breakfast has been associated with a 27% increased risk of heart disease, a 21 % higher risk of type 2 diabetes in men, and a 20% higher risk of type 2 diabetes in women.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 不吃早餐会使患上心脏病的风险增加27%，男性患 II 型糖尿病的风险增加21%，女性患 II 型糖尿病的风险增加20%。

examination_example.sentence: She still remembers the sting of her first experience <highlight>skipping</highlight> an assignment due to the high prices.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她至今还记得第一次因为高价而逃掉任务所经历的痛苦。

sense_info_list.en: move along lightly; stepping from one foot to the other with a hop or bounce

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: bound off one point after another intentionally

examination_example.sentence: Before one of these workouts, the men <highlight>skipped</highlight> breakfast, meaning that they exercised on a completely empty stomach after a long overnight fast.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在其中一项训练之前，这些人跳过吃早餐，这意味着他们在经过一整夜的禁食后，完全空腹进行锻炼。

examination_example.sentence: The implication of these results is that to gain the greatest health benefits from exercise, it may be wise to <highlight>skip</highlight> eating first.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些结果表明，为了从运动中获得最大的健康益处，最好先不吃东西。

examination_example.sentence: The men displayed lower blood sugar levels at the start of their workouts when they had <highlight>skipped</highlight> breakfast than when they had eaten.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这些人不吃早餐就运动的血糖水平低于吃过早餐再运动的。

sense_info_list.en: to not do something that you usually do or should do

examination_example.sentence: While <highlight>skipping</highlight> rope, you have to move rapidly.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 跳绳时，你必须快速移动。

examination_example.sentence: Among its findings was the fact that students who shared a main meal with their families were less likely to <highlight>skip</highlight> school.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 研究发现，与家人共享一顿主餐的学生逃学的可能性更小。

examination_example.sentence: Mary stopped <highlight>skipping</highlight> and spoke to the robin.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 玛丽停止了蹦蹦跳跳，和知更鸟说话。
玛丽在花园里跳来跳去。
